metadata.description:
This token is created based on the original CloneX NFT named "CloneX #16349" [ https://opensea.io/assets/ethereum/0x49cf6f5d44e70224e2e23fdcdd2c053f30ada28b/3271 ]

Bring the community. Let's own a CloneX NFT - together.

Hold onto this token and use it to swap for an actual fraction of the CloneX #16349 NFT when Frac's F-NFT DEX launches in Feb to March 2023! The DEX will allow buyers and sellers to trade fractions of NFTs!

These NFTs can either represent virtual art, membership or even physical assets.
metadata.name: CloneX F-NFT Token
